  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0b89\u0bb2\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd  \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8 ; \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Laying paddy rice on the street without a place to dry it; Farmers are worried",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "Farmers in Dharmapuram area, where small-scale training has been carried out under the Kalmadu Nagar pond, have expressed concern that there is no place to dry rice paddies lying on the road.",
        "We block the road and let the paddy dry because we don't have a paddy drying platform of our own. At present, due to continuous rains, there is a situation of lying on the road at night.",
        "Currently, due to fuel shortage in the country, traders who buy paddy from outside districts have to dry paddy on the street even after 15 days of harvest because they cannot get the fuel they need.",
        "Therefore, in this regard, the concerned authorities are requesting the Kamakkara organizations under Kalmadu Pond to take appropriate steps to sell the harvested paddy and help them to improve their livelihood."
      ],
